** {{tcond|If the player has lost the Blindweed seed:}}
*** '''Player:''' And what happens if I lose the seed?
*** '''Captain Braindeath:''' Then I'll have ye flogged, hung, slapped with a haddock and sent back out there to fight the zombie hordes with little more than harsh language!
*** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
