===Talking to Davey===
* '''Player:''' Hello!
* '''Davey:''' 'Ello guv.
* '''Player:''' Why are you not helping out the others?
* '''Davey:''' Well you see, guv, I've got these unshakable religious convictions.
* '''Player:''' And those are?
* '''Davey:''' Well, it's like this, see. I used to do a bit of the old priestin' on the side.
* '''Davey:''' You know, collectin' for repairs to the church roof, passing the collection plate, jumble sales, nicking the lead off the temple roof so they needed repairing again.
* '''Davey:''' Real holy stuff, you know.
* '''Player:''' That doesn't sound all that holy to me.
* '''Davey:''' Well, that's because you're not a man of the cloth are you?
* '''Davey:''' You are, in fact, what we refer to in layman's terms as a punter.
* '''Davey:''' But anyway, all that priestin' left me with an unshakable faith in three things.
* '''Davey:''' The power of good over evil.
* '''Davey:''' The true glory of the human spirit.
* '''Davey:''' And that I ain't goin out there with those things runnin' around.
* {{tact|end}}

